    "description": "Serving coffee in complete chaos, &quot;Coffee, Plis&quot; shows a crazy day of service in all the coffee shops in the city. Being able to play alone or with friends all you have to do is serve customers as quickly as possible.<br><br><strong>Work as a team</strong><br><br>Being able to play with up to 4 players, synchronization is essential, because in this game, more players make the challenge of not making a big mess even greater!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/648f6b484b58dd011ebfee0fe396b3d8.poster.avif?t=1764391738\" width=400 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/648f6b484b58dd011ebfee0fe396b3d8.webm?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/648f6b484b58dd011ebfee0fe396b3d8.mp4?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Find your style of seeing to customers</strong><br><br>Pay attention to customers and their behavior, as each one has their own way of dealing with the wait. The only thing that is certain is that everyone loves a hot cup of coffee (yes, the coffee gets cold, so be quick).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/2f22b1d1b96f5619379fc673f2c8fe6e.poster.avif?t=1764391738\" width=400 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/2f22b1d1b96f5619379fc673f2c8fe6e.webm?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/2f22b1d1b96f5619379fc673f2c8fe6e.mp4?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/5ce8ff276245853ac61c68c74637a16d.poster.avif?t=1764391738\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/5ce8ff276245853ac61c68c74637a16d.webm?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/5ce8ff276245853ac61c68c74637a16d.mp4?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Be ready for anything!</strong><br><br>Serving is naturally challenging, and it gets even worse at peak hours, with a random customer system every time you start a game it will be a new experience. Various types of orders and a high chance of dropping everything will make customers furious! Be very attentive! Don’t screw up, new kid!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/a3a1eeae384cdc19cdfcb0d1c5003e30.poster.avif?t=1764391738\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/a3a1eeae384cdc19cdfcb0d1c5003e30.webm?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/a3a1eeae384cdc19cdfcb0d1c5003e30.mp4?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Increasing challenges</strong><br><br>The more stars you earn from customer reviews, the more challenges are unlocked, testing your skill even more, have fun finding out your limits!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/ceddf5e7e59a4275c9156fa7c55c4346.poster.avif?t=1764391738\" width=400 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/ceddf5e7e59a4275c9156fa7c55c4346.webm?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381430/extras/ceddf5e7e59a4275c9156fa7c55c4346.mp4?t=1764391738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
